{"tid":2159972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（零確診喎）支那男偷渡入越南後確診 疫控單位：幸及時發現","createTime":"2020-08-16T16:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T18:19:02.000Z","uid":50386,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6eca61f5c06ee055ff915bb54f73c6d9dd5cc4","tid":2159972,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"越南政府日前公布一宗中國偷渡客確診的消息，一名 27 歲的男子在上月 27 日和其他 7 名同鄉偷渡進入越南北部，然後坐車前往胡志明市；他到達後被當地警方拘捕，並被送往隔離，經核酸檢驗後在本月 12 日確診。<br />\n<br />\n據英文《越南快訊》（VnExpress）報道，越南政府 14 日公布國內新增 18 宗確診個案，其中一例為非法入境的中國人，他在 7 月 27 日與另外 7 名同鄉從越南北部偷渡，然後坐車共三天車程前往胡志明市；抵達的隔日就被警方發現予以逮捕，並被送往第 7 區的醫院進行隔離與檢驗，最後在 8 月 12 日確診，目前正在古芝野戰醫院（Cu Chi Field Hospital）接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7%E5%81%B7%E6%B8%A1%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E5%BE%8C%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%96%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D-%E5%B9%B8%E5%8F%8A%E6%99%82%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE-%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E9%87%80%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E5%2589%2587%25E9%2587%2580%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=9cbe4a5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258D%259